---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy Policy for Chiltern Computers - How we handle your personal data and protect your privacy."
>
  <div class="section-bg-1" style="padding: 120px 20px 80px; min-height: 100vh;">
    <div class="container">

      <!-- Page Header -->
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 60px;">
        <h1 class="space-font galaxy-text cosmic-glow" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 6vw, 48px); margin-bottom: 16px;">
          Privacy Policy
        </h1>
        <div style="height: 3px; width: 120px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--plasma-cyan), var(--aurora-green)); margin: 0 auto 20px; border-radius: 2px;"></div>
        <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--comet-silver); font-size: 16px; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
          Last updated: January 2025
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Privacy Content -->
      <div class="cosmic-card" style="padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">1. Introduction</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Chiltern Computers ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our services or visit our website.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">2. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            We may collect the following types of information:
          </p>
          <ul class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 24px;">
            <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and postal address when you contact us or request a service.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Details about the computer or device you bring in for repair, including make, model, and serial number.</li>
            <li><strong>Service Records:</strong> Information about repairs performed, parts used, and service history.</li>
            <li><strong>Communication Records:</strong> Records of correspondence between you and Chiltern Computers.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            We use your personal information to:
          </p>
          <ul class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 24px;">
            <li>Provide computer repair and IT support services</li>
            <li>Communicate with you about your service requests</li>
            <li>Send invoices and process payments</li>
            <li>Maintain records for warranty purposes</li>
            <li>Improve our services based on feedback</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">4. Data on Your Devices</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            When you bring a device in for repair, we may need to access files and data for diagnostic purposes. We do not copy, retain, or share any personal data from your devices unless specifically required for the repair and agreed with you in advance. We strongly recommend backing up your data before any repair work.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">5. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            We take reasonable measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction. Customer records are kept securely and are only accessible to authorized personnel.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">6. Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            We retain customer records for as long as necessary to provide our services and fulfill legal obligations. Service records are typically kept for 6 years for warranty and accounting purposes. You may request deletion of your personal data at any time, subject to legal requirements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">7. Third-Party Sharing</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for marketing purposes. We may share information with service providers who assist in our operations (such as payment processors) or when required by law.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">8. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 12px;">
            Under UK data protection law (UK GDPR), you have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-left: 24px;">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data (where applicable)</li>
            <li>Object to processing of your data</li>
            <li>Request data portability</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">9. Cookies and Website Analytics</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Our website may use essential cookies to ensure proper functionality. We do not use tracking cookies or third-party analytics that collect personal data without consent.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="terms-section">
          <h2 class="space-font" style="color: var(--aurora-green); font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px;">10. Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy or wish to exercise your data protection rights, please contact us:
          </p>
          <div style="background: rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.1); border: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan); border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin-top: 12px;">
            <p class="alien-font" style="color: var(--starlight-white); font-size: 14px; margin: 0;">
              Chiltern Computers<br>
              38 Hilldene Avenue, Harold Hill, Romford, Essex, RM3 8YP<br>
              Email: david@chilterncomputers.net<br>
              Phone: 07971 331814
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid var(--plasma-cyan);">
          <a href="/contact/" class="space-button">
            <span>Contact Us</span>
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
